{"tid":1877960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"各國封關　TVB：美星兩國拒送陸港澳郵件","createTime":"2020-02-13T10:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:12:13.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8a8a854e6be8e69305f39af19ab6eaebba85a2","tid":1877960,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1275472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F1275472&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=33f95d3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/1275472</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情蔓延，全球好幾家航空公司宣布暫停往返大陸航班，但也造成全球包裹、信件運送混亂，美聯社報導，美國郵政總局11日決定，將不再接受寄往大陸和港澳郵件，新加坡郵政也跟進美國，同樣宣布不再寄送陸港澳相關郵件和包裹。"}]}